# Local maintainer dev workspaces — not part of the published package.
# These contain vendored 3rd-party clones and debugging scratchpads kept
# only on the maintainer's disk. Anything in here would otherwise leak
# into the Comfy Registry archive (where the registry's static scanner
# would count their `NODE_CLASS_MAPPINGS` against this pack — see
# CHANGELOG entry for v0.1.4 for the full back-story).
